<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Features</title>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %> <!-- Ensure Bootstrap CSS is included -->
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <%- include("partials/nav.ejs") %> <!-- Navigation bar -->
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">Features of ArgoVenture</h1>
        <p>ArgoVenture is a comprehensive platform designed to help users discover, collaborate on, and manage projects efficiently. Below are some key features of ArgoVenture:</p>

        <h2>Project Discovery</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Explore a wide range of projects spanning various industries and interests.</li>
            <li>Discover projects based on categories, tags, or keywords.</li>
            <li>View detailed project descriptions, including goals, requirements, and deadlines.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Collaboration Tools</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Connect with like-minded individuals and potential collaborators.</li>
            <li>Join existing projects or create new ones to pursue your interests.</li>
            <li>Communicate with team members through built-in messaging and chat features.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Project Management</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Organize project details, tasks, and milestones in a centralized dashboard.</li>
            <li>Set deadlines, assign tasks, and track progress in real-time.</li>
            <li>Receive notifications and updates on project activities and milestones.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>User Profiles</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Create personalized profiles to showcase skills, experience, and interests.</li>
            <li>Highlight past projects, contributions, and achievements.</li>
            <li>Connect with other users and build a network of collaborators and mentors.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Security and Privacy</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Ensure data security and privacy with robust encryption and access controls.</li>
            <li>Manage permissions and access levels for project participants and collaborators.</li>
            <li>Comply with data protection regulations and standards to safeguard user information.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <footer class="container mt-4">
        <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %> <!-- Footer -->
    </footer>
    <!-- Toggle Theme Button placed at the bottom-right of the page -->
    <div id="themeToggle" style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px;">
        <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary" id="toggleTheme">Dark Mode</button>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/theme.js"></script> <!-- Theme Script -->
    <!-- Bootstrap JS Bundle with Popper -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
